Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有麻將的將
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的前世是冉·阿讓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:37.23,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(496,436)}Jean-Valjean
